the same values as we have just looked at and all work the same way,

00:03:25.700 --> 00:03:28.625
but this time on the opposite axis.

00:03:28.625 --> 00:03:34.415
The next two properties we apply to the child items to control them individually.

00:03:34.415 --> 00:03:37.825
Let's re-introduce our item one class.

00:03:37.825 --> 00:03:40.800
This can be any of the items.

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:45.965
Let's just add this in and then we can control these one individual item.

00:03:45.965 --> 00:03:49.190
