00:03:49.190 --> 00:03:55.230
justify items, and also align items too so that they don't interfere.

00:03:55.430 --> 00:04:00.470
Now we can go back up to the item one and then we can

00:04:00.470 --> 00:04:06.035
align individual item but this time we use justify itself.

00:04:06.035 --> 00:04:10.665
Let's begin with end and then over to the browser,

00:04:10.665 --> 00:04:14.160
refresh and because this also works on the row,

00:04:14.160 --> 00:04:17.355
this pushes this blue item to the end.

