00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:29.330
It is now we have all these items,

00:04:29.330 --> 00:04:33.800
set the stretch, and then this individual item on the end of the row.

00:04:33.800 --> 00:04:39.685
Center will also do as expected and move this one item into the middle of the row.

00:04:39.685 --> 00:04:41.805
Changes to be center,

